title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS TOYOTA HILUX/FORTUNER – FUEL MANAGER FM628DPK PRE FILTER WATER SEPARATOR KIT

content.rendered:
WESTERN FILTERS TOYOTA HILUX/FORTUNER – FUEL MANAGER PRE FILTER WATER SEPARATOR KIT FM628DPK

Western Filters Toyota Hilux/Fortuner Fuel Manger Pre Filter Water Separator Kit FM628DPK available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Fuel Manager Fuel Filter / Water Separator Kit for:

  • 2016 Toyota 2.8L Hilux D-4D
  • Toyota Fortuner N80 GUN-126R
  • For both single and duel battery models

This Filter unit is to be used as a Pre Filter to separate water and contaminates thus avoiding costly repairs due to poor fuel quality. Kit includes very detailed fitting instructions and everything you will need and even where to fit it !

Kit Includes:

  • 1x Filter assembly 30 Mic (1x) – Made by Stanadyne in the USA (Filters down to 30 Microns!)
  • Spare Filter (x1)
  • 10mm Fuel Hose 1x 1mtr
  • Bracket (x1)
  • Required fittings: (x22) Plugs, adaptors, barb fittings, adaptors, bolts, nuts, washers, clamps, ziptie
  • Thread Paste Sealant (6ml Tube)

To view the full range of products available for your Triton, CLICK HERE!
